	'/api/disciplines/3ae13b18/': {"id": "3ae13b18", "name": "Cyklistika", "short_name": null, "details": "**Ruprecht** po otvoren\u00ed chcel dok\u00e1za\u0165, \u017ee vie discipl\u00edny organizova\u0165 r\u00fdchlo. Preto sa na v\u00e1s val\u00ed v nen\u00e1vratnej r\u00fdchlosti spolu s bicyklom.\r\n\r\n### Cyklistika bola presunut\u00e1 na sobotu 30. 9.\r\n\r\nCyklistika sa kon\u00e1 *~~23.9.~~* **30.9.** Stret\u00e1vame sa o **9:00** na **Partiz\u00e1nskej l\u00fake**. O **11:30** bude hromadn\u00fd zjazd z kamz\u00edka. \r\n**Kv\u00f4li bezpe\u010dnostn\u00fdm d\u00f4vodom sk\u00f4r nikto od\u00eds\u0165 nem\u00f4\u017ee!**\r\nP\u00f4jdu sa dve trasy simult\u00e1nne. Jedna po asfaltke (pre cestn\u00e9 bicykle), druh\u00e1 po zemine (pre horsk\u00e9 bicykle). Preto z ka\u017edej triedy p\u00f4jdu dvaja cyklisti (ka\u017ed\u00fd na jednu trasu).\r\n\r\nHorsk\u00e1 trasa: [http://mapy.cz/s/fujojecepo](https://mapy.cz/s/fujojecepo)\r\n\r\nCestn\u00e1 trasa: [http://mapy.cz/s/kumanopesa](http://mapy.cz/s/kumanopesa)\r\n\r\n##### \u010co si treba prinies\u0165:\r\n- Cyklistick\u00fa prilbu\r\n- F\u013ea\u0161u vody, ktor\u00fa budete ma\u0165 povinne pri sebe po\u010das pretekov\r\n- Adekv\u00e1tny bicykel (na horsk\u00fa trasu v\u00e1s s cestn\u00fdm nepust\u00edme) s funguj\u00facimi brzdami\r\n- N\u00e1hradn\u00fa du\u0161u vyhovuj\u00facu v\u00e1\u0161mu bicyklu\r\n\r\n**V pr\u00edpade, \u017ee organiz\u00e1tori pos\u00fadia, \u017ee bicykel alebo prilba neodpovedaj\u00fa z\u00e1kladn\u00fdm bezpe\u010dnostn\u00fdm po\u017eiadavk\u00e1m, budete z pretekov vyl\u00fa\u010den\u00fd!**\r\n\r\n**Ke\u010f\u017ee predpovede po\u010dasia nevyzeraj\u00fa najlep\u0161ie (mo\u017eno bude pr\u0161a\u0165), tak do \u0161tvrtka 21.9. do 18:00 d\u00e1me fin\u00e1lny verdikt, \u010di sa cyklistika uskuto\u010dn\u00ed v horeuvedenom term\u00edne, alebo sa presunie na neskor\u0161\u00ed term\u00edn.**\r\n\r\n\u010eakujeme, va\u0161i cykloorgovia.", "date": "2023-09-30", "start_time": "09:00:00", "end_time": "12:00:00", "location": "Partiz\u00e1nska l\u00faka", "category": 3, "target_grades": [2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/ed27c161/': {"id": "ed27c161", "name": "Divok\u00fd z\u00e1pad", "short_name": null, "details": ",,Zasa zmizli, zas tu nie s\u00fa!\u201d U\u017e tradi\u010dne sa oz\u00fdvaj\u00fa hlasy v hlave na\u0161emu netradi\u010dn\u00e9mu kamar\u00e1tovi. Ale tentokr\u00e1t m\u00e1 pravdu. Kde s\u00fa orgovia? V\u0161etci netradi\u010dn\u00ed akoby sa vyparili. No a kto ich n\u00e1jde? Uh\u00e1dli ste, budete to vy!\r\n\r\nV **utorok 24.10.** sa uskuto\u010dn\u00ed discipl\u00edna **Divok\u00fd z\u00e1pad**. Va\u0161ou \u00falohou bude chodi\u0165 po starom meste a foti\u0165 sa s orgami. Discipl\u00edny sa m\u00f4\u017eu z\u00fa\u010dastni\u0165 maxim\u00e1lne **traja** \u013eudia. Na discipl\u00ednu potrebujete nabit\u00fd mobil so stiahnut\u00fdm Instagramom a mobiln\u00fdmi d\u00e1tami na posielanie fotiek. Stretneme sa o **15:50 na \u0161kolskom dvore**. Bli\u017e\u0161ie pravidl\u00e1 bud\u00fa ozn\u00e1men\u00e9 na mieste.\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na v\u00e1s. Va\u0161i orgovia.", "date": "2023-10-24", "start_time": "15:50:00", "end_time": "18:00:00", "location": "\u0160kolsk\u00fd dvor", "category": 4, "target_grades": [2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
