	'/api/disciplines/0a5b02d6/': {"id": "0a5b02d6", "name": "T\u00e9matick\u00e9 dni", "short_name": null, "details": "Ahojte,\r\n\r\nposledn\u00e9 t\u00fd\u017edne sa Bla\u017eej so sklaman\u00edm prizeral na monot\u00f3nnos\u0165 \u0161kolsk\u00fdch dn\u00ed. Rozhodol sa teda, \u017ee ich p\u00f4jde postr\u010di\u0165 smerom k nev\u0161ednosti.\r\n\r\nPo\u010das nasleduj\u00facich dvoch t\u00fd\u017ed\u0148ov sa teda postupne uskuto\u010dnia 4 t\u00e9matick\u00e9 dni.\r\n\r\n#### T\u00c9MY:\r\n\t3.10 - Anime\r\n\t5.10 - Met\u00e1l\r\n\t10.10 - 1920s\r\n\t12.10 - Hippie style\r\n\t\r\nKa\u017ed\u00fd z t\u00fdchto spomenut\u00fdch dn\u00ed bude teda Va\u0161ou \u00falohou obliec\u0165 \u010do najviac \u013eud\u00ed z triedy do tematick\u00fdch kost\u00fdmov, a pripravi\u0165 si kr\u00e1tku, jeden- a\u017e dvojmin\u00fatov\u00fa sc\u00e9nku, ktor\u00fa si cez prest\u00e1vky pr\u00edde pozrie\u0165 komisia zlo\u017een\u00e1 z orgov a u\u010dite\u013eov. Rozpisy kontr\u00f4l bud\u00fa zverej\u0148ovan\u00e9 priebe\u017ene.\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na Va\u0161e kost\u00fdmy a sc\u00e9nky,\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia.", "date": "2023-10-03", "start_time": null, "end_time": null, "location": "Gam\u010da", "category": 4, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/7defb873/': {"id": "7defb873", "name": "Programovanie", "short_name": null, "details": "Po tom ako si Korn\u00e9lia vysk\u00fa\u0161ala svoje schopnosti z informatiky na papieri by si chcela vysk\u00fa\u0161a\u0165 aj rie\u0161i\u0165 re\u00e1lne probl\u00e9my. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nPreto sa v pondelok **20. 11.** sa po\u010das **2. a\u017e 4. hodiny** uskuto\u010dn\u00ed programovanie (miestnos\u0165 bude \u0161pecifikovan\u00e1 nesk\u00f4r). Pr\u00edd\u0165e u\u017e na za\u010diatok prest\u00e1vky aby sme vedeli \u010do najsk\u00f4r za\u010da\u0165. P\u00f4jde o algoritmick\u00e9 programovanie ako m\u00f4\u017eete pozna\u0165 zo s\u00fa\u0165a\u017e\u00ed OI, KSP, Zenit, ...  \r\nSilne v\u00e1m odpor\u00fa\u010dame **donies\u0165 si vlastn\u00fd notebook**. Pravdepodobne sa bude da\u0165 po\u017ei\u010da\u0165 aj nejak\u00e9 \u0161kolsk\u00e9 ale nezaru\u010dujeme na nich dostupnos\u0165 a funk\u010dnos\u0165 programovac\u00edch jazykov alebo IDE\u010diek.  \r\n*Napr. C++ sa v\u00e1m pravdepodobne nepodar\u00ed rozbeha\u0165 na \u017eiadnom \u0161kolskom po\u010d\u00edta\u010di.*", "date": "2023-11-20", "start_time": "08:35:00", "end_time": "11:30:00", "location": null, "category": 1, "target_grades": [2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
