	'/api/disciplines/76559bdb/': {"id": "76559bdb", "name": "3D", "short_name": null, "details": "Ahojte,\r\n\r\nArno\u0161t si mysl\u00ed, \u017ee zm\u00fd\u0161\u013eanie gam\u010d\u00e1kov je u\u017e op\u00e4\u0165 len jednoduch\u00e9 rovinn\u00e9. Pripravil si pre V\u00e1s preto v\u00fdzvu, ktor\u00e1 preberie Va\u0161e kockat\u00e9 hlavy.\r\n\r\nPripom\u00edname teda, \u017ee u\u017e tento **pondelok, 9.10**., je term\u00edn odovzdania 3D.\r\n\r\nMateri\u00e1l, technika a rozmery s\u00fa \u013eubovo\u013en\u00e9 (v r\u00e1mci mo\u017enosti), okrem materi\u00e1lov, ktor\u00e9 m\u00f4\u017eu zhni\u0165, pokazi\u0165 sa, at\u010f. Va\u0161e s\u00fa\u0165a\u017en\u00e9 v\u00fdtvory prineste pros\u00edm v pondelok **do 14:00 do Septimy A**. Nesk\u00f4r u\u017e nevieme zaru\u010di\u0165, \u017ee n\u00e1s n\u00e1jdete. \r\n\r\n#### T\u00c9MY:\r\n\tStarovek\u00ed bohovia\r\n\tStrom \u017eelan\u00ed \r\n\tTrochu viac lepidla pros\u00edm\r\n\tToto v encyklop\u00e9dii nen\u00e1jde\u0161\r\n\tKlenoty pre kr\u00e1\u013eovn\u00fa\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na Va\u0161e v\u00fdtvory,\r\n\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia!", "date": "2023-10-09", "start_time": null, "end_time": null, "location": null, "category": 2, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/82de718f/': {"id": "82de718f", "name": "GP (2. Stupe\u0148)", "short_name": null, "details": "#### Ahojte, Bla\u017eej u\u017e m\u00e1 pocit, \u017ee mlad\u0161ie obyvate\u013estvo Gam\u010de za\u010d\u00edna upada\u0165 nasp\u00e4\u0165 do f\u00e1dnej norm\u00e1lnosti. Preto si pre V\u00e1s pripravil ve\u013ek\u00fd test, v ktorom sa sna\u017e\u00ed zisti\u0165, nako\u013eko ste ochotn\u00ed vyst\u00fapi\u0165 zo svojich rut\u00edn.  \r\nTento test sa sa uskuto\u010dn\u00ed u\u017e **tento \u0161tvrtok**. Svoju cestu budete **za\u010d\u00edna\u0165 aj kon\u010di\u0165** na **Gam\u010di**, pr\u00ed\u010fte akoby ste i\u0161li na **prv\u00fa hodinu**.  Predpokladan\u00fd koniec je okolo 12tej.\r\n\r\n#### POZOR! Nastali zmeny v zozname vec\u00ed. Zmeny s\u00fa vyzna\u010den\u00e9 boldom.\r\n\r\nNezabudnite si so sebou donies\u0165 aj tieto veci:\r\n- \u010co najviac **plaveck\u00fdch** okuliarov\r\n- **1** Twister\r\n- **1** \u0161achovnicu s **33** fig\u00farkami\r\n- **1** futbalov\u00fa loptu\r\n\t- Po\u010das presunu ju budete musie\u0165 nosi\u0165 v ta\u0161ke\r\n- **Pr\u00e1ve jeden** model \u013eudsk\u00e9ho org\u00e1nu\r\n- **1.5** anglick\u00e9ho ro\u017eka\r\n- **2** Mickey Mouse DVD\r\n- Aspo\u0148 **3** litrov\u00fa zatvar\u00e1ciu n\u00e1dobu s vodou (nem\u00f4\u017ee by\u0165 sklenen\u00e1)\r\n- **5** sne\u017eiacich gul\u00ed\r\n-  To\u013eko fotiek \u013eud\u00ed z triedy pri Slav\u00edne (vytla\u010den\u00e9, musia na nich by\u0165 rozdielni \u013eudia), ko\u013eko je trpasl\u00edkov\r\n- **11** cestovn\u00fdch l\u00edstkov \u0161tiknut\u00fdch po 19:59\r\n- ***ne\u0161\u0165astn\u00e9 \u010d\u00edslo*** gumov\u00fdch ka\u010diek\r\n- **15** metrov v **3** metrov\u00fdch \u0161pag\u00e1toch\r\n- **17** Rubikov\u00fdch kociek\r\n- **19** dopravn\u00fdch m\u00e1p\r\n- \u0160atku pre ka\u017ed\u00e9ho (a dve navy\u0161e)\r\n- **73** fixiek\r\n- **151** kociek lega\r\n- \u010co najviac sticky notov\r\n- Nieko\u013eko \u0161krabiek na zemiaky\r\n- Ka\u017ed\u00e9mu aspo\u0148 jeden uter\u00e1k (mus\u00ed ho ma\u0165 vidite\u013ene na sebe)\r\n- **1** Lightsaber\r\n- Vec na sedenie pre ka\u017ed\u00e9ho\r\n\t- Ka\u017ed\u00fd vlastn\u00fa, t.j. nem\u00f4\u017ee sedie\u0165 viac \u013eud\u00ed na jednej veci\r\n\t- Mus\u00edte ich vedie\u0165 rozumne nies\u0165, \u010di\u017ee napr. stoli\u010dky s\u00fa povolen\u00e9 iba ak s\u00fa skladacie\r\n- \u010co najv\u00e4\u010d\u0161\u00ed kus molit\u00e1nu s maxim\u00e1lnou ve\u013ekos\u0165ou 0.5 m\u00b3\r\n- **1** volant", "date": "2023-09-21", "start_time": "07:50:00", "end_time": "12:00:00", "location": "Gam\u010da", "category": 4, "target_grades": [1], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
	'/api/disciplines/6dae8b27/': {"id": "6dae8b27", "name": "Atletika", "short_name": null, "details": "**Ruprecht** si uvedomil, \u017ee spolu s orgami **nem\u00f4\u017eu pred probl\u00e9mami oh\u00e1\u010dky nav\u017edy uteka\u0165**- my\u0161lienky sk\u00e1\u010du \u010faleko do dia\u013eky a chaos vrh\u00e1 na orgov tmav\u00fd tie\u0148. Na nastolenie poriadku mysle sa teda rozhodol u\u017e tento v\u00edkend zorganizova\u0165 atletiku- uteka\u0165 bud\u00fa len gam\u010d\u00e1ci a vrha\u0165 sa bude iba gu\u013eou. \r\n\r\nStretneme sa v nede\u013eu **8.10. v are\u00e1li Mladej gardy**! \r\n\r\n2.stupe\u0148: 9:00- 10:45, stretnutie: meetup 8:45  \r\n3.stupe\u0148: 10:45- 14:00, stretnutie: 10:30\r\n\r\nZ\u00e1kladn\u00e9 pravidl\u00e1 sa dozviete na mieste. Medzi be\u017ecami \u0161tafety mus\u00ed be\u017ea\u0165 aspo\u0148 jedna \u017eena.\r\n\r\n**Discipl\u00edny** a ich **rozpis** n\u00e1jdete v [tomto dokumente](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Y9iLML2CqC0tk7cbax0A85icrAFuH9nrbZqGb4o59uk/edit?usp=sharing \"tomto dokumente\").\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na V\u00e1s,  \r\nVa\u0161i orgovia.", "date": "2023-10-08", "start_time": "09:00:00", "end_time": "14:00:00", "location": "Mlad\u00e1 Garda", "category": 3, "target_grades": [1, 2], "is_public": true, "date_published": true, "details_published": true, "results_published": true, "result_details": ""},
