	'/api/posts/8f9aef67/': {"id": "8f9aef67", "title": "DTN (De\u0148 tradi\u010dn\u00fdch netradi\u010diek)", "content": "Ahojte,\r\nu\u017e zajtra (8.9), po otvoren\u00ed sa uskuto\u010dn\u00ed DTN v na\u0161ej milovanej ve\u013ekej telocvi\u010dni. Bude sa s\u00fa\u0165a\u017ei\u0165 vo f\u013euse \u017euva\u010dkou (s\u00fa zabezpe\u010den\u00e9 ru\u017eov\u00e9 orbitky, no k\u013eudne m\u00f4\u017eete pou\u017eit aj vlastn\u00e9), \u017eonglovan\u00ed loptou (tak\u00e9 to kopanie, nie ru\u010dn\u00e9), kope papu\u010dou do br\u00e1nky a hode gum\u00e1kom.\r\nNa 3. stupe\u0148 sa te\u0161\u00edme hne\u010f po otvoren\u00ed o 12:45 a\u017e do 13:30, a na 2. stupe\u0148 si po\u010dk\u00e1me o 13:30 a potrv\u00e1 to do 13:45. \r\nVa\u0161i Orgovia.", "safe": false, "redirect": null, "author": {"id": 34, "username": "Juraj Helbich", "first_name": "Juraj", "last_name": "Helbich", "type": "organiser"}, "date": "2023-09-07T21:23:59.051354+02:00", "related_disciplines": ["d813e243"], "affected_grades": [1, 2], "tags": [2]},
