	'/api/posts/a9829f8a/': {"id": "a9829f8a", "title": "Galaprogram", "content": "Ahojte, prin\u00e1\u0161ame V\u00e1m inform\u00e1cie o Galaprograme.\r\n\r\nGalaprogram sa bude kona\u0165 vo \u0161tvrtok 7. 12. v troch  r\u00f4znych \u010dasoch. Galaprogram pre druh\u00fd stupe\u0148 bude o 8:30, pre tret\u00ed stupe\u0148 o 11:00 a pre verejnos\u0165 o 15:00.\r\n\r\nPlaten\u00fd Galaprogram je ur\u010den\u00fd pre verejnos\u0165 (rodi\u010dov, zn\u00e1mych alebo exgam\u010d\u00e1kov) a l\u00edstky na\u0148 si m\u00f4\u017eete k\u00fapi\u0165 ni\u017e\u0161ie. V\u0161etci \u017eiaci \u0161koly bud\u00fa ma\u0165 Galaprogram zadarmo.\r\n\r\nVa\u0161i orgovia\r\n\r\n<script type='text/javascript' src='http://ajax.aspnetcdn.com/ajax/jQuery/jquery-1.6.min.js'></script><div style='text-align:center'><iframe id='tpiframe1' name='tpiframe1' src='https://www.ticketportal.sk/event.aspx?id=820474&iframe&idpartner=971' width='100%' height='800px' frameborder='0'></iframe>", "safe": true, "redirect": null, "author": {"id": 1, "username": "Jakub \u0160iagi", "first_name": "Jakub", "last_name": "\u0160iagi", "type": "admin"}, "date": "2023-11-23T20:56:12.480884+01:00", "related_disciplines": [], "affected_grades": [1, 2, 4, 5], "tags": []},
