	'/api/posts/caec16fa/': {"id": "caec16fa", "title": "Dlhodob\u00e1 zbiera\u010dka", "content": "Ahojte,\r\n\r\nv\u0161etok vedeck\u00fd v\u00fdskum sa raz dostane k svojmu koncu, a Korn\u00e9lia V\u00e1s teda pros\u00ed o odovzdanie Va\u0161ich nadobudnut\u00fdch poznatkov.\r\n\r\nU\u017e zajtra, 21.11., preto pros\u00edm prineste Va\u0161e nazbieran\u00e9 n\u00e1lepky od ovocia v po\u017eadovanom form\u00e1te (na prilo\u017eenej mrie\u017eke) do Septimy A. KA\u017dD\u00dd PAPIER MUS\u00cd BY\u0164 PODP\u00cdSAN\u00dd MENOM VA\u0160EJ TRIEDY. Nepodp\u00edsan\u00e9 papiere nebudeme hodnoti\u0165, rovnako tak ani papiere nesp\u013a\u0148aj\u00face form\u00e1tov\u00fa normu.\r\n\r\nTe\u0161\u00edme sa na V\u00e1\u0161 zber,\r\n\r\n Va\u0161i orgovia!", "safe": false, "redirect": null, "author": {"id": 7, "username": "Lucia Chladn\u00e1", "first_name": "Lucia", "last_name": "Chladn\u00e1", "type": "organiser"}, "date": "2023-11-20T21:10:10.534727+01:00", "related_disciplines": ["593bff99"], "affected_grades": [1, 2], "tags": []},
