	'/api/posts/39c392ea/': {"id": "39c392ea", "title": "\u0160ifrova\u010dka - 4. t\u00fd\u017ede\u0148", "content": "Ahojte,\r\ndnes bola zverejnen\u00e1 \u0161tvrt\u00e1 a posledn\u00e1 sada \u0161ifier pre druh\u00fd stupe\u0148. Spolu s \u0148ou sme zverejnili aj n\u00e1povedy k tretej sade \u0161ifier.\r\n\r\nOspravedl\u0148ujeme sa za trochu neskor\u0161ie zverejnenie \u0161ifier, org ktor\u00fd ich nahadzuje v\u010dera akt\u00edvne rie\u0161il probl\u00e9m s nedostatkom sp\u00e1nku.\r\n\r\nChceli by sme e\u0161te raz pripomen\u00fa\u0165 mo\u017enos\u0165 hodnotenia \u0161ifier. Boli by sme naozaj radi keby ste ju vyu\u017eili a k hodnoteniu nap\u00edsali aj nejak\u00fd koment\u00e1r. Nemus\u00edte sa b\u00e1\u0165 aj kritizova\u0165, body v\u00e1m za to nestrhneme, je to iba informa\u010dne pre n\u00e1s.\r\n\r\nOkrem \u0161ifier m\u00e1me pre v\u00e1s aj priebe\u017en\u00e9 v\u00fdsledky:\r\n\r\n|  | Trieda | Vyrie\u0161en\u00e9 \u0161ifry | \u0160ifry vyrie\u0161en\u00e9 pred n\u00e1povedou | Po\u010det dn\u00ed do vyrie\u0161enia | Nespr\u00e1vne rie\u0161enia | Celkov\u00fd \u010das do vyrie\u0161enia |\r\n| :------------ | :------------ | :------------ | :------------ | :------------ | :------------ | :------------ |\r\n| **1.** | Tercia A | 12 | 10 | 36 | 1 | 3716793 |\r\n| **2.** | Pr\u00edma A | 12 | 10 | 38 | 1 | 4037896 |\r\n| **3.** | Kvarta B | 8 | 6 | 37 | 38 | 3614258 |\r\n| **4.** | Kvarta A | 8 | 5 | 32 | 5 | 3180513 |\r\n| **5.** | Pr\u00edma B | 8 | 4 | 56 | 4 | 5308628 |\r\n| **6.** | Sekunda A | 6 | 3 | 32 | 35 | 3171031 |\r\n\r\n***Po\u010det dn\u00ed a celkov\u00fd \u010das do vyrie\u0161enia sa r\u00e1taj\u00fa iba z vyrie\u0161en\u00fdch \u0161ifier.***", "safe": false, "redirect": null, "author": {"id": 1, "username": "Jakub \u0160iagi", "first_name": "Jakub", "last_name": "\u0160iagi", "type": "admin"}, "date": "2023-10-16T09:08:17.445171+02:00", "related_disciplines": ["0107583d"], "affected_grades": [1], "tags": [4]},
